it for you to save your friends, if you're too slow they may be gone forever.<br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1126640/extras/5431f58326590e7e69d092a9959daa66.poster.avif?t=1680509281\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1126640/extras/5431f58326590e7e69d092a9959daa66.webm?t=1680509281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1126640/extras/5431f58326590e7e69d092a9959daa66.mp4?t=1680509281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
